          "id": "hi-fi-rush-studio-tango-gameworks-has-been-acquired-by-kraft",
          "title": "Hi-Fi Rush studio **Tango Gameworks** has been acquired by Krafton and will remain open",
          "body": null,
          "url": "https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/hi-fi-rush-studio-tango-gameworks-has-been-acquired-by-krafton-and-will-remain-open/",
